        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Powered by GPT-4o, our Resume Plan Generator is completely free, with no word limits, subscription fees, or hidden costs. Create unlimited resume plans for various industries, roles, and career paths without restrictions.</p>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Each resume plan includes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="text-lg">Recommended sections tailored to your target job</li>
          <li class="text-lg">Key achievements and skills to emphasize</li>
          <li class="text-lg">Formatting suggestions for maximum impact</li>
          <li class="text-lg">ATS (Applicant Tracking System) optimization tips</li>
          <li class="text-lg">Everything you need to create a resume that stands out in today's competitive job market</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">How to Create Your Perfect Resume Plan in Minutes</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Using the Resume Plan Generator is simple and fast:</p>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Enter Your Job Target Details</span>
            <p>Specify your target job title and industry to ensure your resume plan is focused and relevant.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Share Your Experience and Skills</span>
            <p>Outline your professional background and highlight key competencies for a more personalized resume plan.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Add Optional Personalization</span>
            <p>Provide role level (entry-level, mid-career, executive) and education details to tailor your resume plan even further.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Generate and Implement Your Resume Plan</span>
            <p>Click generate and receive a strategic, customized blueprint you can immediately put into action.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Why Strategic Resume Planning Leads to More Interviews</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Stand Out Instantly</h3>
            <p>A strategically crafted resume, built from your Resume Plan Generator output, places your most impactful achievements front and centerâ€”essential for catching a recruiter's eye in under 7 seconds.</p>
          </div>
          
