        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Recent Graduates:</span> Emphasize education, internships, and transferable skills.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Career Changers:</span> Reframe your experience to align with new industry expectations.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Mid-Career Professionals:</span> Focus on your most impactful achievements.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Executives:</span> Strategically highlight leadership, vision, and key accomplishments.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Returning to Work:</span> Address employment gaps with strength and confidence.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Troubleshooting: Getting the Best Results with the Resume Plan Generator</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Issue</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Solution</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
