                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Include the exact job description you're targeting for sharper, role-specific advice.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Missing industry-specific advice?</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Specify niche industries (e.g., "Healthcare IT" instead of just "Technology").</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions About the Resume Plan Generator</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
